                                                                                                                                                   [1m[43;3H1. Swim Meet Photography (Parent-Pay Model)[22m[21X[45;3HThis[1Cis[1Cthe[1Ckey[1Cinsight[1C--[1m[1Cparents[1Cpay[1Chim[1Cdirectly[22m[1Cto[1Cphotograph[1Ctheir[1Ckids[1Cat[1Cmeets.[1CThey[1Csign[1Cup[1Cin[1Cadvance[1Cbefore[1Craces.[1CThe[1m[1Cclub[1Cpays[46;3Hnothing[22m[1C--[1Cthey[1Cjust[1Cprovide[1Cdeck[1Caccess,[1CWiFi,[1Cand[1Cpromote[1Cthe[1Cservice.[1CIn[1Creturn,[1Cthe[1Cclub[1Cgets[1Ca[1Ccommercial[1Clicense[1Cto[1Call[1Cpurchased[1Cimages[47;3Hfor[1Ctheir[1Cwebsite/social[1Cmedia.[1CSome[1Cclubs[1C(like[1CMississauga[1CAquatic[1CClub)[1Chave[1Ca[1m[1Cfundraising[1Crevenue-share[22m[1Cwhere[1Cthe[1Cclub[1Cearns[1Ca[1Ccut[1Cof[1Cparent[48;3Hpurchases.[1CIt's[1Cbasically[1Cthe[1Cschool[1Cportrait[1Cphotography[1Cmodel[1Cadapted[1Cfor[1Cswim[1Cmeets.[1m[50;3H2.[1CCommercial/Corporate[1CWork[1C(Likely[1CHis[1CPrimary[1CIncome)[22m
